updated_at: "2026-05-16T23:59:58.135Z"
author: maintainer-agent
acceptance_criteria: PRs run 2-entry matrix (ubuntu+macos on Node 20); main push runs the full 5-entry matrix; nightly continues full matrix; documentation reflects this in CONTRIBUTING.md.
parent: pm-tzwy
resolution: "Implemented event-aware GitHub Actions matrix: pull_request runs ubuntu-latest/macOS Node 20 only; main push keeps full five-job matrix."
expected_result: PRs run 2-entry matrix; main pushes run full five-entry matrix; nightly remains unchanged; CONTRIBUTING documents behavior.
actual_result: "Focused CI contract, linked pm test, isolated dogfood, static/secret/typecheck, full release gate, Sentry, and telemetry checks passed."
